<gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be given</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">thrown away,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ ταῦτα προεῖτ᾽ ἀκονιτεί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:200\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.200</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καιροὶ προεῖνται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg019.perseus-grc1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.8</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg025.perseus-grc1:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.10</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n87558.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπὶ τὸ αὐτίκα ἡδὺ π. αὑτούς</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">devote</tr_> themselves to . . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:7:5:76\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">Cyr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.5.76</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n87558.8\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in Prose mostly in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram> </gramGrp> (not found in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">send forward from oneself, drive forward,</tr_> <ci