.9</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κλημάτια . . προϊέμενα ῥίζας</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dsc.\">Dsc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.29</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n87558.11\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give up, let go,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προέμενον αὐτῇ</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὴν χεῖρα</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:121\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.121</biblScope></bibl>.<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">έ;</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give up</tr_> to the enemy, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Κέρκυραν τοῖς Κορινθίοις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.44</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.72</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:213\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.213</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">abandon,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg019.perseus-grc1:152\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.152</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. σφᾶς αὐτούς</fore